<h1 style="color:Tomato;">Information Regarding Online free Courses, Hackathons and Various Scholarships</h1>
<h2 style="color:MediumSeaGreen;">Free Courses during this Corona Pandemic</h2>
<p>There are so many online learning platform which are providing various free certification courses during this Corona Pandemic.</p>
<h3 style="color:Brown;">Coursera</h3>
<p1>Coursera is a world-wide online learning platform founded in 2012 by Stanford professors Andrew Ng and Daphne Koller that offers massive open online courses, specializations, and degrees.</p1></br>
</br>
<p2>Coursera is making a selection of courses completely free for anyone, anywhere so itâ€™s easier to keep learning. While many courses on Coursera are already available for free without a certificate, this promotion enables you to not only access lectures and quizzes, but also to earn a free certificate for courses that offer them.</p2>
<p>Below are some courses offered by Coursera:-</p>
<a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/gcp-fundamentals-aws?">Google Cloud Platform For AWS Professionals From Google</a></br>
<p3>This course introduces AWS professionals to the core capabilities of Google Cloud Platform (GCP) in the four technology pillars: networking, compute, storage, and database. It is designed for AWS Solution Architects and SysOps Administrators familiar with AWS features and setup and want to gain experience configuring GCP products immediately. With presentations, demos, and hands-on labs, participants get details of similarities, differences, and initial how-tos quickly. If you prefer to learn fast by doing, this course is for you.</p3></br>
</br>
<a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/cloud-computing-basics?">Cloud Computing Basics(Cloud 101) From LearnQuest</a></br>
</p4>Cloud computing is a model for enabling ubiquitous, convenient, on-demand network access to a shared pool of configurable computing resources (e.g., networks, servers, storage, applications, and services) that can be rapidly provisioned and released with minimal management effort or service provider interaction.</p4></br>
</br>
<a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/android-app?">Build Your First Android App</a></br>
</p5>An Android app is a software application running on the Android platform. Because the Android platform is built for mobile devices, a typical Android app is designed for a smartphone or a tablet PC running on the Android OS.In this course, you will learn about how to build your android app.</p5></br>
</br>
<a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/career-advancement?">Successful Carrer Development</a></br>
<p>No matter the professional level,we can all benefit from learning how to succeed in our careers. Whether a well-seasoned professionals,a management trainee,or a service level employee,this course will help you enrich your career by honing your professionals behaviour and networking.</p>
<h3 style="color:Brown;">Udemy</h3>
<a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/html5-fundamentals-for-begineers/">HTML5 and CSS3 Fundamentals</a></br>
<p>Build your very own website with HTML5 from scratch using HTML5 and CSS3 - designed for complete beginners</p></br>
<a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/programming 101/">Programming 101</a></br>
<p>Comprehend basic foundational knowledge of hardware, networking, programming and licensing.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/manageyourtime/">A Mini Course on Time Management</a></br>
<p>Time management is the process of planning and exercising conscious control of time spent on specific activities, especially to increase effectiveness, efficiency, and productivity.</p>
<p>In this course, you will learn about 7 steps to become more productive and master time management.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/quick-to-working-remotely-from-vp-of-learning/">best practices for working remotely</a></br>
<p>In this course, you will learn how to use frequent communication to stay connected and social with your colleagues,Structure your workday to maximize your time and many more.</p>
</br>
<h2 style="color:MediumSeaGreen;">Hackathons</h2>
<a href="https://www.sih.gov.in">Smart India Hackathon</a></br>
<p>Smart India Hackathon is a nationwide initiative to provide students with a platform to solve some of the pressing problems we face in our daily lives, and thus inculcate a culture of product innovation and a mindset of problem-solving.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.msazurevirtualhack.com/">Microsoft Azure Virtual Hackathon</a></br>
<p>This virtual hackathon aims to bring together AI/ML enthusiasts, talented developers, designers, and entrepreneurs to solve real-world business challenges from APAC using Azure AI. With multiple partner challenges, our goal is for participants to use Azure technology to create something innovative and transformative.</p></br>
<a href="https://githubhackathon.com/">Github Hackathon:Build Something new with us</a></br>
<p>This four-week hackathon challenges the community to create original GitHub Actions. Actions connect all of the tools in your workflow: You can solve problems, build containers, deploy to any cloud, and more.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.gitlab.com/community/hackathon/">Gitlab Hackathon</a></br> 
<p>The Hackathon is a virtual event open to anyone who is interested in contributing code, documentation, translations, UX designs and more to GitLab.</p></br>
<h2 style="color:MediumSeaGreen;">Various Scholarship</h2>
<a href="http://kvpy.iisc.ernet.in/main/fellowship.htm">Kishore Vaigyanik Protsahan Yojna Fellowship</a></br>
<p> The Kishore Vaigyanik Protsahan Yojana (KVPY) is an on-going National Program of Fellowship in Basic Sciences, initiated and funded by the Department of Science and Technology, Government of India, to attract exceptionally highly motivated students for pursuing basic science courses and research career in science.</p></br>
<a href="https://nst.onlinetestseriesmadeeasy.in/">National Scholarship Test-NST (MADE EASY)</a></br>
<p>National Scholarship Test (NST) is an initiative of MADE EASY to inspire and support the talented students; to chase their dream career, overcoming the financial hurdles.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.aicte-jk-scholarship-gov.in/">Prime Minister Special Scholarship Scheme (PMSSS)</a></br>
<p>J & K Cell deals with Implementation of Prime Ministers Special Scholarship Scheme to J & K Students to pursue undergraduate studies outside the State of Jammu and Kashmir.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.aiysee.com/">All India Youth Scholarship Entrance Examination (AIYSEE)</a></br>
<p>AIYSEE is a national level scholarship program that provides financial assistance to the meritorious students so as to fulfill their academic dreams.</p></br> 
<a href="https://www.aictsd.com/aryabhatta-national-maths-competition/">Aryabhatta National Maths Competition</a></br>
<p>The Aryabhatta National Maths Competition is a part of the mission launched by the All India Council for Technical Skill Development. The main aim of this competition is to develop and create leaders at an academic level in the country.</p></br>
<a href="https://sfp.iitm.ac.in/">IITM Summer Fellowship Programme</a></br><p>Indian Institute of Technology, IIT Madras has invited applications for two months of  Summer Fellowship program 2020. The program is designed to enhance the awareness in academic research of Engineering, Management and Humanities students.</p></br>
<a href="https://www.licindia.in/Bottom-Links/Golden-Jubilee-Foundation/Scholarship">LIC Golden Jubilee Scholarship</a></br>
<p>The objective is to award scholarships to meritorious students belonging to economically weaker families to provide them with better opportunities for higher education and thus enhance their employability.</p></br>
<a href="https://v1.hdfcbank.com/htdocs/common/ECSS_scholarship.htm">HDFC Educational Crisis Scholarship Support</a></br>
<p>HDFC Educational Crisis Scholarship Support (ECSS) invites applications from students who are in excessive need for financial support. The programme helps students from Class 6th to post-graduate levels that are at a risk of dropping out due to their financial condition.</p>
